# FREAK LITE BIBLE
## The Complete Reference for Building the FREAK → C Transpiler
### Version: Alternative-4 Edition | Status: Authoritative

---

## WHAT YOU ARE BUILDING

FREAK Lite is a subset of the FREAK programming language that transpiles to C.
The output C is then compiled by GCC or Clang to produce a native binary.

Pipeline:
  .fk source → Lexer → Parser → Type Checker → C Emitter → Clang/GCC → binary

You (Opus) are being asked to help build this transpiler in Python.
The transpiler itself is written in Python. The language it compiles is FREAK.
The output it produces is C.

