## SECTION 10: BUILD INVOCATION

After emitting the C file:

```bash
# Debug build
clang -o output output.c freak_runtime.c -I. -g

# Release build
clang -O2 -o output output.c freak_runtime.c -I.

# Or GCC
gcc -O2 -o output output.c freak_runtime.c -I.
```

The transpiler should offer to run this automatically after emitting.

