## END OF FREAK LITE BIBLE

This document is the complete reference for building FREAK Lite v1.
Start with the lexer. Get it tokenizing basic programs.
Then the parser. Then a minimal C emitter that handles variables and functions.
First goal: `pilot x = 42` and `say "Hello, {x}"` compiling to working C.
Everything else builds from there.

Good luck. The Hangar doors are open.
